---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/vue/Footer.vue';
import Header from '../components/vue/Header.vue';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - PM-Panel">
    <!-- Header -->
    <Header client:only="vue" />

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="legal-content">
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 2024</p>

                <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>PM-Panel respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our project management platform.</p>

                <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
                <h3>2.1 Account Information</h3>
                <p>When you register, we collect your name, email address, and password (encrypted). This information is necessary to create and manage your account.</p>

                <h3>2.2 Project Data</h3>
                <p>We store project names, client information, status updates, notes, and file attachments that you create within the platform. This data is isolated per project and owned by you.</p>

                <h3>2.3 Usage Data</h3>
                <p>We collect basic analytics such as page views and feature usage to improve our service. We do not use tracking pixels or third-party analytics that follow you across the web.</p>

                <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>To provide and maintain the PM-Panel service</li>
                    <li>To notify you of updates, security alerts, or support messages</li>
                    <li>To improve our platform based on usage patterns</li>
                    <li>To prevent fraud and ensure platform security</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>4. Data Storage & Security</h2>
                <p>Your data is stored in secure databases with encryption at rest. Each project can optionally use isolated tenant databases for enhanced data separation. We implement industry-standard security measures including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>HTTPS encryption for all data transmission</li>
                    <li>Password hashing using bcrypt</li>
                    <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
                    <li>Access controls and authentication checks</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>5. Data Ownership & Deletion</h2>
                <p>You own your data. You can delete projects, notes, and your entire account at any time. When you delete a project using a tenant database, that database and all its data are permanently removed.</p>

                <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
                <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Turso</strong> — Database hosting and edge distribution</li>
                    <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — CDN and DDoS protection</li>
                </ul>
                <p>These services are GDPR-compliant and process data only as necessary to provide our platform.</p>

                <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
                <p>We use minimal cookies:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Session cookie</strong> — Keeps you logged in</li>
                    <li><strong>Theme preference</strong> — Remembers your dark/light mode choice</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.</p>

                <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Access your personal data</li>
                    <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
                    <li>Delete your data</li>
                    <li>Export your data</li>
                    <li>Object to certain processing</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>For privacy-related questions or requests, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@pm-panel.com">privacy@pm-panel.com</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <Footer client:only="vue" />
</Layout>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="/fix.css">

<style>
    .section {
        padding: 60px 0;
    }

    .legal-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .legal-content h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .last-updated {
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .legal-content h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
        margin-top: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .legal-content h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    }

    .legal-content p {
        color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .legal-content ul {
        padding-left: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .legal-content li {
        color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        padding: 4px 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .legal-content a {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .legal-content h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
        }
    }
</style>
